## Print frame (non-negotiable)

| Constant | Value |
|---|---|
| Card size | **2.5″ × 3.5″** (240×336px at 96dpi) |
| Overflow | `overflow: hidden` on `.card` |
| Proof pages | **`height: 3.5in`** — never `min-height` (min-height makes cards look taller than print) |
| idtag clearance | `card-body` / `.cbody` **`padding-bottom: 26–32px`** for absolute `.idtag` |

If text clips, **rewrite copy or line-break** — do not rely on negative margins, arbitrary indents, or
hiding the idtag. The bottom-left **class idtag** (e.g. **Paladin**) is required on class Core cards.

