## Extending to other Core cards

- **Patron** (Warlock): separate builder pattern; 3×2 mark grid — do not blindly copy Oath grid.
- **Loadout / Bulwark:** simpler `.card-body` prose — still respect print frame + idtag.
- New dense Core UI: prototype on proof page first; add `scripts/build_<name>_html.py` when the layout
  stabilizes; patch `card-data.js` via dedicated `patch_card_data_*.py` when possible.

